<AbstractNarration>This proposal was received in response to NSE, NSF-0019.   The award supports the construction and application of an electric Stark-effect coupled infrared near field microscope.  This will be a powerful new tool for the analysis of the chemical composition of surface nanostructures on 50-100 nm length scales, which are the critical scales for polymer nanotechnologies.</AbstractNarration>
